OL,7,FA body is believed to be inside a
OL,8,Fderelict bar in Hanley, , which was
OL,9,Fdestroyed by a fire earlier this week.
OL,11,Fsays it believes someone may have died
OL,12,Fin the blaze in the former Yates's.
OL,14,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,15,Fbuilding on Brockley Square at around
OL,16,F5.45am on Tuesday 12 March, with
OL,17,Faround 60 firefighters tackling the
OL,18,Fblaze.
