OL,7,FThe building remains too unsafe to
OL,8,Fenter, as firefighters continue to
OL,9,Fdampen down the site.
OL,11,FA man, 63, of no fixed address, was
OL,12,Farrested on suspicion of attempted
OL,13,Farson with intent to endanger life,
OL,14,Fand remains in custody.
OL,16,FA woman, 33, from Stoke-on-Trent, who
OL,17,Fwas arrested on suspicion of the same
OL,18,Foffence, has been released on
OL,19,Fconditional police bail while
OL,20,Finquiries continue.
