OL,7,FStaffordshire Police said: "The large
OL,8,Fcordon at the scene of a fire in
OL,9,FHanley is still in place today as we
OL,10,Fcontinue to search the area and appeal
OL,11,Ffor information. Officers have been
OL,12,Fworking alongside colleagues from
OL,13,FStaffordshire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,14,Fsince the first call came in at 5.45am
OL,15,Fon Tuesday.J"Once we're able to safely
OL,16,Fgo inside the building, we will be
OL,17,Fcompleting a thorough search alongside
OL,18,Ffire investigators to determine the
OL,19,Fcause of the blaze.J"We're aware of
OL,20,Freports suggesting there might be a
OL,21,Fbody inside the building. At this
OL,22,Ftime, we can sadly confirm that we
OL,23,Fbelieve there is a body inside, but
OL,24,Fwe're unable to carry out a search
OL,25,Funtil the area is deemed safe. We will
OL,26,Fshare updates as soon as we're able
