OL,7,FA Staffordshire Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FService spokesman said: "We are
OL,9,Fcontinuing to dampen down hotspots at
OL,10,Fa disused nightclub in Hanley. Up to
OL,11,F60 firefighters have been working
OL,12,Faround the clock to contain the fire
OL,13,Fsince it was first reported at 5.45am
OL,14,Fon Tuesday.J"As soon as it's safe to
OL,15,Fdo so, we'll be entering the building
OL,16,Fto carry out an investigation into the
OL,17,Fcause of the fire. The cordon is still
OL,18,Fin place in the area alongside our
OL,19,Fcolleagues from Staffordshire Police."
